OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny early
OL,6,Fshowers will soon clear in the
OL,7,Fevening. Cloud will then increase from
OL,8,Fthe evening as outbreaks of rain push
OL,9,Feast overnight, some of which will be
OL,10,Fheavy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with patchy rain at
OL,13,Ffirst, this soon clearing, becoming
OL,14,Fmostly dry with bright spells and a
OL,15,Ffew afternoon showers.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,18,Fspells interspersed with showers
OL,19,FMonday. Cloudy with rain, some heavy,
OL,20,Ffor a time early Tuesday and again
OL,21,Flater Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
